~ start
if GameState.loaded_save_data["sewer_path"] < 2:
	=> open_grate
if GameState.loaded_save_data["sewer_path"] == 2:
	=> closed_grate
~ open_grate
: There is a drainage grate connecting to the vault. It appears to be screwed shut.
if GameState.player_has_item("Screwdriver"):
	: Unlock the grate?
	- Yes
		: The grate is unlocked!
		do GameState.send_to_vault("sewer_path")
	- No
		=> END
=> END
~ closed_grate
: The drainage grate seems to be completely covered. It appears that the vault is no longer capable of handling drainage as a result.
=> END